<item>
            <title>[LU-16945] sanity test_27Cg: timeout when running in interop mode</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16945</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;adilger@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/518ae7e9-ea71-4133-871f-affeadf6ec72&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/518ae7e9-ea71-4133-871f-affeadf6ec72&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_27Cg failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Timeout occurred after 112 minutes, last suite running was sanity
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4415&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4415&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-425.10.1.el8_7.x86_64 (2.12.9)&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_12/164&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_12/164&lt;/a&gt; - 3.10.0-1160.49.1.el7_lustre.x86_64 (master)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/50487&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/50487&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16693&quot; title=&quot;file creation with not existent OST gets hung&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-16693&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-16693&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; lod: ENODEV on setstripe with wrong OST#&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; landed in commit &lt;tt&gt;v2_15_55-80-gd96b98ee6b&lt;/tt&gt; fails 100% in interop mode because it tries to create an invalid file layout, but the error return code &lt;tt&gt;-ENODEV&lt;/tt&gt; from an old server will be retried indefinitely by the client.  The patch fixes the server to return &lt;tt&gt;-EINVAL&lt;/tt&gt;, but that fix is not present on old servers, so the subtest needs to be skipped in this case.&lt;/p&gt;







&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
sanity test_27Cg - Timeout occurred after 112 minutes, last suite running was sanity&lt;/p&gt;</description>
